        Advanced Search. The use of post is mostly for the sequence string for blast which can get very long and results in a 413 status code if sent via GET
        Parameters:
        searchWeb - whether to perform a web of registry search or not
        query - parameters to the search
        Returns:
        results of the search

        Keyword search
        Parameters:
        queryString - keywords to search on
        searchWeb - whether to perform a web of registry search or not
        offset - result start
        limit - result count upper limit
        sort - result sort
        asc - true if return results in ascending order, false otherwise
        Returns:
        wrapper around list of search results conforming to query params
